ecoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3761670" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Bon-Jovi-Forever-2024-Credit-Jacquet-Droz.jpg" alt="乔恩·邦·乔维（Jon Bon Jovi）2024。" width="2000" height="3000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Bon-Jovi-Forever-2024-Credit-Jacquet-Droz.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Bon-Jovi-Forever-2024-Credit-Jacquet-Droz-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Bon-Jovi-Forever-2024-Credit-Jacquet-Droz-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Bon-Jovi-Forever-2024-Credit-Jacquet-Droz-696x1044.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Bon-Jovi-Forever-2024-Credit-Jacquet-Droz-1392x2088.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Bon-Jovi-Forever-2024-Credit-Jacquet-Droz-1068x1602.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3761670" class="wp-caption-text">乔恩·邦·乔维（Jon Bon Jovi）2024年。信用：雅克·德罗兹（Jacquet Droz）</figcaption></figure><p>乔恩·邦·乔维（Jon Bon Jovi）多次说过，直到他回来100％的健康状况，他才能回到舞台上。</p><p> “当我们刚开始时，滚石乐队刚满40岁，我们以为它们年纪大了，但是他们仍将标准设置为今天。那个乐队是榜样，不仅对我们，而且是追随我们的一代人。”他透露。 “看看<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-mccartney">保罗·麦卡特尼（Paul McCartney）</a> ，他81岁，仍在制作纪录。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-springsteen">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀（Bruce Springsteen）</a>在74岁时举行三个半小时的音乐会，仍在他妈的火。人们不希望您成为平均水平。”</p><p>他继续说：“我永远不想成为胖猫王。他去世时只有42岁，因为他没有任何人提供帮助。他在毒品和酒中被肿，只是一个他妈的火车残骸。我不是那样的，很简单。您向那些前来的人学习。”</p><p>邦·乔维（Bon Jovi）承认“每天努力努力变得更好”时，“不确定性是可怕的”，他说他只会把自己完全扔到某事中，或者每天称其为一天。</p><p>他说：“我确实知道的一件事是，在做出决定后，当我将头放在枕头上时，将对决定有100％的信心。” “加入摇滚乐队永远不会感到安全。这不是终身句子，而是时间的时刻。”</p><p>近年来，像<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/abba-voyage-live-in-london-review-photos-video-setlist-2-3235227">Abba Voyage Avatar Show</a>这样的事情在巡回演出后为乐队带来了生活 - <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-first-kiss-avatar-shows-will-take-place-in-2027-3562981">Kiss</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-elvis-ai-hologram-show-more-like-time-travel-than-abba-voyage-says-creator-3567189">Elvis Productions在路上使用类似的全息图技术</a>。似乎并非不太可能看到接下来几年的Bon Jovi类似的东西。</p><p> Bon Jovi解释说：“我不反对它，因为这是一个自动点唱机。这与广播中听音乐的人没有什么不同。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C7jwljKOUUq/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.